replies.body:
i think the low logic from sometimes very smart individuals comes from influence of other games, where you want to have the most powerful items, and you're always the hero; never the loser. so why waste gold on potions when you're supposed to always win and have the strongest items? it's very different if you never played a moba and league is the first one for you, eventually they do learn the usefulness of potions or defensive items and defensive playing if they're critical of themselves before being critical of others, and actively trying to learn from the game (which is hard to do to yourself, and hard when people are flaming you and you're trying to prove them wrong, leading to a constant downhill of bad choices)

just my input on the whole thing, since me and my friends came from other games directly into league and skipping through the tutorial 
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
